* Iron Raptor looked back down at her hands for a moment, everything still 
seeming so new, then looking down at her body.
White hair did cover most of it, only seeing blue gaps and her legs.
Otherwise...she was naked....
She sighed, thinking openly, how could she ever go back to base like this?
But then, a little tired of sitting, Iron Raptor slowly got to her 
feet...only to end up on her rear again.
She sighed.*

" I'm not use to these legs."

* But then Iron Raptor looked up at Prowl, still seeing him as new and 
fairly different.*

" Thoughts...telepathy?"

* She moved a strand of hair out of her way, thinking about just what Prowl 
had just said.
Feel his thoughts, like he could feel hers.*

" I've seen...your thoughts. The Matrix...and the deal you made."

* But then her features turned softer, remembering just why Prowl had made 
that head after the merge had gone back.*

" You did that for me?"

* But also, something poped up in her mind, a thought which was loud and 
clear. What was it that had triggered the detination, to make the merge go 
wrong?*
